<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>A Quill district admin account was created for you. As an admin of <%= @district_name%>, you will have district-wide access to teacher accounts and student reports for your district. </p>

<p>🛎️ <strong>Complete your account setup</strong></p>

<p>To complete your account setup, please set a password.<p>

<a href=<%= @set_password_link%>>Set my password and log in</a>

<p>ℹ️ <strong>How to log in using Google or Clever</strong></p>

<p>You can link your account with Google or Clever to make it easier to log in. Confirm with your admin your school or district’s preference, and then <a href=<%= @constants[:links][:link_account]%> rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">complete the steps in this guide</a>.</p>

<p>ℹ️ <strong>How to access the School Dashboard</strong></p>

<p>When you log in to your account, you will see a “School Dashboard” tab. This tab will show you a list of all teachers who have signed up for Quill at your school.</p>

<a href=<%= @constants[:links][:admin_dashboard]%> rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">View the School Dashboard</a>

<p>ℹ️ <strong>Need help?</strong></p>

<p>If you have any questions or issues with your account, please reply to this email. You can also <a href=<%= @constants[:links][:premium]%> rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">learn more about Quill Premium here</a>.</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>

<p><%= @constants[:signatures][:quill_team]%></p>
